  <summary>3/19/1987--Introduced.
Directs the Attorney General to develop a reporting system for the acquisition of data about crimes which manifest racial, ethnic, or religious prejudice. Requires the Attorney General to publish an annual summary of such data. Authorizes appropriations for FY 1988 through 1992.</summary>
